title: Driving time (min) to nearest FQHC
name: FqhcTmDr
description: Driving time from tract/zip origin centroid to the nearest tract/zip FQHC destination centroid, in minutes
source_long: United States Covid Atlas via Health Resources and Services Adminsitration, 2020
comments: This dataset includes all US states, Washington D.C., and Puerto Rico. It does not include the territories Guam, Northern Mariana Islands, American Samoa, Palau. Zip code and tract centroids are not population-weighted.
